Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan, you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A-Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I-I-In... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've raised Ryuuji-kun well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I-I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The reason why my life was in "danger"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}L-Listen, Ya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After falling for the fake voicemail that Taiga left,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko cried a lot and Grandpa scolded her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somehow, it's like Ya-chan is a child right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Families are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though they haven't seen each other in about ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}they're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mom, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all because of you spoiling Yasuko{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, there's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.50,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're a family, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji-kun, hurry up and take your bath before the water gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you weren't married...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your dad ran away with another woman while I was pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though everyone told me to get an abortion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the end, I couldn't protect you and things broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't Grandma say you raised me well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See, I'm a lot taller than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your back was really big when you were running...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So big that I didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was really scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I was also a little happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I was so afraid that you'd leave and never come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you left by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm the last person who should say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but running away won't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll do it right in front of you, not in some place far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why you have to look at me... always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandma said there's nothing wrong with sleeping in the same room since we're going to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now I understand how Yasuko became the way she is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ya-chan is laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are a lot of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be honest, I'm kind of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think running away and getting married will work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I still want to have this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I feel like if I don't do something here, things will break again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, you and Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing broke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, it's okay for us to start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't need to run away to get married. Let's do it with everyone's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wouldn't it be best to receive everyone's blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who do you mean by "everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa, Grandma and your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That will take a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since we'll be happy anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}why not share our happiness with everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but before that, let's have a little rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... I, Takasu Ryuuji, will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't matter, just say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-How can it not matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... will marry Aisaka Taiga{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I thought, I don't want a vow yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?! Wasn't this your idea in the first{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you remember what you said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Since ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast to equal the tiger."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why, even without a vow, we'll always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your eyes are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your breathing is all weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your lips are cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll hurt if we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we kiss, it'll definitely hurt... a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just as I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was like a rough, dry wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, it was really, really warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, it's cold, so let's do it one more{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somehow, it feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just us two left,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but now three people and a pet are coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji, you believed it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That Ya-chan would come if you lied,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then get back on good terms with Grandma and Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't think she would,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I didn't think she wouldn't either...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps families are like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga-chan, you're coming over for dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're a family of three, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I forgot about you, Inko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.82,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{w}Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys go ahead, I'm going to go change my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But won't your parents be{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be quick, since I'm making your favorite tonight; pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, what are you think{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You seriously don't think about the consequen{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cut it ou{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga... do you really hate me that mu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't give a damn anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm leaving, so do whatever you want! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's just like a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always thought that I would never be loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not just making pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandma taught me how to make some delicious taro rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Ryuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...but perhaps that was just an excuse for running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't see the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's hidden and lonely, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I blamed my lack of confidence on my parents and my surroundings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but Ryuuji still loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to accept everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will be proud of myself and love Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That day, Taiga didn't come over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu, we can't understand if you don't tell us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What actually happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did Taiga{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, everyone, back to your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have some bad news for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Due to family reasons, Aisaka-san is withdrawing from this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've just received that message from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka-san will be going back to her mother's{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wai{\fscx300}-{\fscx100} This is a lie, right? It's a joke, right? She was forced, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She didn't tell us or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In your lives, you will all come to different crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Regardless of if you decide to stay where you are or turn back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you still have to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka-san's decision may mean leaving you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it's a decision she tried her best to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's support her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kids these days are so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you all calling Aisaka-san? Texting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should all take a good, hard look at your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.44,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{w}Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.67,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It won't go through if we all call at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{w}Everyone, back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushie{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.93,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you clench your teeth for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you come back by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is Taiga transferring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Takas{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I... I didn't want her to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd bring her back right now if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd ask her why she decided everything by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}she believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why the only thing I can do right now is accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, she learns how to be tidy at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh! A single sock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's your buddy? I'll definitely find him for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That clumsy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How could she forget these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're really stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I remember when I fell into the river{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was interrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh, I even said it a few times to Kawashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I can be really stupid sometimes too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tomiya-kun, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's somewhere I want to go, can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I'm sorry for yesterday."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then why are you telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think I kind of understand what you said now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey! Taiga's text message!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It seems like Taiga replied to everyone who texted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is it just a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that small dot a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really? You're imagining things, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's definitely a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But why did she take a picture of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I will protect you all from the faraway sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up! She's not dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she means, "I'll try my best."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Even if the sky is pitch black, with nothing to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there will be stars shining somewhere out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I keep shining brighter and brighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll definitely look better to people."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think Taiga is kind of selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But even if that's the case, the sky will connect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As long as we all shine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}no matter how far apart we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we will definitely be able to see each other doing our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You overdid that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It sent chills down my spine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the feeling of being young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me too! I'll be happy if she's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of stars, someone caused a lot of trouble back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After taking the time to send us this, I think she'd be happy if we replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I remember putting it away with Ami-chan's tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You think of these things to make others happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I put it... You're amazing at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My existence itself should be surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, before she became who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}people loved her even though she caused trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was jealous of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though she seems amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}her body and heart are both so small and timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All she does is take whatever people throw at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She won't let anyone see her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's the same as {\i1}someone{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, she was seen through from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't you say I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, I hate myself when I pretend to be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I'm desperate to have others accept me for who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I finally understood after meeting Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As long as there's at least one person who understands me, I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if it isn't love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kawashima{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I found the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I just have to press here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss, please hurry up before my godlike power runs out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, Takasu-kun. Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Smile already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Amin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast to equal the tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you're not by my side right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will leap through space and time and always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These feelings will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Inko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't this makeup a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a mother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I should just use some softer colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I don't have things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-Inko-chan finally said his own name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be lonely once the seniors leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're all so cool and interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you know that our student council president, Kitamura-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}will be studying abroad in America after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The president and the seniors made the Cultural Festival and the Sports Festival amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I heard that the previous cultural festival was even more amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was the legendary one where 2-C won everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! It was all because of the Palmtop something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Palmtop something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You mean the Palmtop Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one who brings you good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That person really exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, the Palmtop Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She went to this school last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moreover, she's Takasu-senpai's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's something in this world that no one has seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It is gentle and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe if it could be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}everyone would fight over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why no one has ever seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world hid it so that no one could get their hands on it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, someday, someone will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The person who deserves it the most will definitely find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was planning to surprise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It seems like you grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not even a millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.07,0:23:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Why would you say something embarrassing like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should've waited for a better mood or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is how it's created.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signs
